id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-20T22:15:37.663111+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":null,"enriched_at":null,"enrichment_cycle":0,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"Forgiveness is a bitter pill to swallow.","homepage":"http://cakemovie.net/","overview":"After having visions of a member of her support group who killed herself, a woman who also suffers with chronic pain seeks out the widower of the suicide."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"עוגה","runtime":0,"tagline":"מחילה היא צפרדע שקשה לבלוע.","homepage":"","overview":"קלייר סימונס היא אישה חריפה ומצחיקה הסובלת מכאבים כרוניים ונוטלת תרופות רבות. לאחר התפרצות שלה בקבוצת התמיכה בעקבות התאבדותה של נינה, חברת הקבוצה, היא מתבקשת להפסיק להגיע לפגישות. קלייר מתחילה לחקור את חייה ומותה של נינה ופוגשת בבעלה. בין השניים מתפתחת מערכת יחסים רומנטית שמתעמתת גם עם רוחה של נינה וגם עם העבר הטרגי המודחק שלה עצמה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Cake - Um Sopro de Vida","runtime":102,"tagline":"O perdão é um remédio difícil de engolir.","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Simmons (Jennifer Aniston) é uma mulher traumatizada e depressiva, que busca ajuda em um grupo para pessoas com dores crônicas. Lá, ela descobre o suicídio de um dos membros do grupo, Nina (Anna Kendrick). Claire fica obcecada pela história desta mulher, e começa a investigar a sua vida. Aos poucos, começa a desenvolver uma relação inesperada com o ex-marido de Nina, Roy (Sam Worthington)."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Bennett ist schwer vom Schicksal getroffen, sie leidet an chronischen Schmerzen und lenkt ihren Frust immer wieder auf die Menschen, die sie umgeben. Freunde und Ehemann haben sich von ihr abgewandt. Als Bezugsperson bleibt nur die Haushälterin Silvana, aber auch sie hat Probleme damit, den Alkohol- und Pillenkonsum ihrer Chefin zu tolerieren. Eine Zeit lang besuchte Claire eine Selbsthilfegruppe – bis sie rausgeworfen wurde. Dort lernte sie Nina kennen, die sich umgebracht hat. Obsessiv versucht Claire, die Umstände des Freitods aufzuklären. Dabei lernt sie Ninas Ehemann kennen, Roy, kommt ihm immer näher und beginnt schließlich eine Affäre mit dem alleinstehenden Mann. Ob die Beziehung hilft, Claires emotionale Wunden zu heilen?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"Le pardon est une pilule amère à avaler.","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Bennett va mal. Il n’y a qu’à voir ses cicatrices et ses grimaces de douleur dès qu’elle fait un geste pour comprendre qu’elle souffre physiquement. Elle ne parvient guère mieux à dissimuler son mal‐être affectif."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Boldogság bármi áron","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire többnyire egyedül tölti napjait a házában, mióta férje otthagyta. Egyetlen barátja a házvezetőnője, akinek fizetnie kell, hogy törődjön vele. Depressziója leküzdése érdekében egy önsegítő csoportba jár. A fiatal Nina szintén ide jár, de most öngyilkosságot követ el. Claire-t egy éjszaka hallucinációk gyötrik, s megjelenik előtte Nina. A nő többet akar megtudni az elhunytról, ezért elmegy a hídra, ahonnan leugrott, illetve a házához is, ahol férjével élt. Az érzelmileg összetört Roy és Claire összebarátkoznak."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"Η συγχώρεση είναι ένα πικρό φάρμακο.","homepage":"http://cakemovie.net/","overview":"Φοβισμένη, ευαίσθητη και κενή συναισθηματικά η πικρόχολη Κλερ (Άνιστον), είναι μια γυναίκα που έχει καταφέρει να τους απομακρύνει όλους από τη ζωή της περνώντας τις μέρες της απομονωμένη στο σπίτι της στο Λος Άντζελες. Παρατημένη από τον άντρα της, παρακολουθεί κάποιες συναντήσεις μίας ομάδας ψυχολογικής υποστήριξης. Όταν όμως μαθαίνει για την αυτοκτονία μιας γυναίκας από το γκρουπ, αρχίζει σταδιακά να συμφιλιώνεται με τη δική της προσωπική τραγωδία, βλέποντας πλέον τη ζωή με διαφορετική ματιά..."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Cake","runtime":102,"tagline":"El perdón es una píldora amarga de tragar","homepage":"http://www.imdb.com/offsite/?page-action=offsite-cakemovie&token=BCYhgqcmCAsnALGNL3P10r8pkfiO3LKpGej2K9MoIwVNHTWJ7qinK1uxB_PIV6cOH5Qh5ry71wKE%0D%0ANoPtcJWS0HkLtOV7UCGW0SCjIHS5mpMa0Lbn74BiWx3B8WH8zqFhNVSJTItxGiI795pzpqmjx4u4%0D%0AaSc31zEgxdZSTQVWZKZgIHLPUrpJi7pUKOUjDVsbzNaFa6b6y1fTRQ7vp_M_trhPeHnVf9A2dJVz%0D%0Ad5Nf-qKfmwU%0D%0A&ref_=tt_pdt_ofs_offsite_0","overview":"Claire (Jennifer Aniston) tiene prácticamente una vida llena de problemas. Lucha día a día para lidiar con el dolor que la está debilitando y después de su divorcio, la última cosa que ella necesita en su vida es el trauma añadido del suicidio de Nina (Anna Kendrik), una mujer del grupo de apoyo al que ella acude.  Mientras Claire lucha por tranquilizarse y combatir los desafíos del día a día, establece un vínculo con su ama de llaves y el ex marido de Nina. Mientras investiga las causas del suicidio de la mujer, se ve incapaz de dar respuesta a sus dudas, sin embargo sí que empieza a servirle de ayuda para apaciguar su propia angustia y comenzar así un lento proceso de curación."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Торт","runtime":98,"tagline":"Торт","homepage":"","overview":"Клэр привлекательная, веселая и острая на язык женщина. В один день она узнаёт о самоубийстве одной из участниц группы психологической поддержки, собрания которой она посещает из-за синдрома хронической боли. Клэр решает узнать историю этой несчастной. Копаясь в жизни покойной, она переживает болезненный роман с вдовцом и сама становится жертвой трагедии."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Bennett is een cynische vrouw die erin is geslaagd om zich te vervreemden van iedereen in haar leven, met uitzondering van haar trouwe huishoudster. Daarnaast raakt ze in de ban van de zelfmoord van een vrouw uit haar praatgroep, mensen met chronische pijn. En hoe meer details ze te weten komt over de zelfmoord, hoe meer ze begint te worstelen met haar eigen"},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"蛋糕","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一场可怕的车祸让克莱尔（詹妮弗·安妮斯顿 Jennifer Aniston 饰）不仅容貌尽毁，还失去了挚爱的儿子，之后，深陷于绝望和痛苦中无法自拔的克莱尔患上了慢性疼痛症。为了同疾病做斗争，克莱尔来到了慢性疼痛俱乐部，通过和病友们的相互交流与鼓励，获得生活下去的信心和希望。  　　妮娜（安娜·肯德里克 Anna Kendrick 饰）是俱乐部中的一员，某日，她自杀身亡的消息震惊了克莱尔。克莱尔想方设法寻求妮娜自杀的真相，最后甚至陷入了同妮娜对话的幻觉之中无法自拔，与此同时，妮娜的丈夫罗伊（萨姆·沃辛顿 Sam Worthington 饰）亦出现在了克莱尔的身旁，将克莱尔卷入了一个又一个漩涡之中。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dort","runtime":0,"tagline":"Odpuštění je hořká pilulka k polknutí.","homepage":"","overview":"Claire (Jennifer Aniston) je členkou terapeutické skupiny pro lidi trpící chronickými bolestmi. Sama trpí následkem autonehody, která jí – kromě jizev na tváří a poškozené páteře – vzala syna, což následně vedlo k rozpadu jejího manželství. Členem její terapeutické skupiny byla i Nina, která však spáchala sebevraždu. To způsobí Claire hluboké trauma, pronásledující ji víc, než si je ochotná připustit. Nina se jí začíná ukazovat jako zjevení, které se jí posmívá. To přiměje Claire k tomu, že se o smrt Niny začne zajímat víc. Nakonec vypátrá její soukromou adresu a spřátelí se s jejím bývalým manželem Royem (Sam Worthington). A potom se stane něco nečekaného..."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire on kroonisista kivuista kärsivänä naisena. Takautumat ja välähdyksinä ilmenevät muistot paljastavat onnettomuuden, joka on vienyt Clairelta niin perheen kuin mielenrauhan."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Bennett frequenta un gruppo femminile di sostegno a persone in depressione ma viene fermamente invitata a lasciarlo dopo le sue reazioni dinanzi al suicidio di una delle componenti, Nina. Claire soffre di dolori terribili, conseguenza di un grave incidente occorsole da più di un anno. Ciò la obbliga ad esercizi di rieducazione e ad imbottirsi di antidolorifici acquistati in modo non sempre legale. A vegliare su di lei, dopo che si è separata dal marito, è la colf messicana Silvana la quale è anche a conoscenza del dolore interiore che la tormenta."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claires kropp är full av ärr, hon har smärta i ben och rygg, mår psykiskt uselt och är känslomässigt tom. Efter en olycka har hon fjärmat både man, vänner och terapeuter. Hon släpper bara in sin trogna hushållerska och ibland trädgårdsmästaren för lite meningslöst sex. Men när en kvinna i terapigruppen begår självmord får Claires liv en annan drivkraft än den som går ut på att ständigt jaga piller."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Cake","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire, toplumdan git gide uzaklaşmış, bungalow'unda kendi kendine yaşayan bir kadındır. Dış dünyayla tek bağlantısı onun her şeyiyle ilgilenen ve aynı zamanda da ona arkadaşlık eden çalışanı Silvana ve katıldığı kronik-ağrılı hastaların oluşturduğu terapi grubudur. Zaman geçtikçe kendisini hayata bağlayan nedenlerin azaldığını düşünürken, terapi grubundaki arkadaşı Nina'nın intiharı hayatını alt üst eder. Birbirlerini çok az tanıyor olmalarına rağmen Nina, Claire'ın rüyalarında hatta sanrılarında bile belirmeye başlar. Claire zamanla Nina'nın ölümünün perde arkasına daha çok kafa yormaya başlar: İntihara hazır olduğunu nasıl anlamıştır? Onu buna iten nedir? Geriye gözü yaşlı bir eş ve bir oğlan çocuğu bırakan Nina'nın hayatı Claire'in git gide daha çok ilgisini çeker. Ancak yaptığı araştırmalarla elde edeceği sonuç hiç de beklediği gibi olmayacaktır.  Filmin yönetmen koltuğunda Daniel Bartz bulunuyor. Başrollerde ise Jennifer Aniston, Anna Kendrick ve Felicity Huffman yer alıyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Simmons uczęszcza na spotkania grupy wsparcia dla osób cierpiących na chroniczny ból. Jedna z jej członkiń, Nina, popełnia samobójstwo. Claire zaczyna interesować się jej przypadkiem. Odkrywając kolejne szczegóły z życia kobiety, nawiązuje bliską relację z mężem nieboszczki, Royem. Jednocześnie boryka się z własną, przeżytą niedawno tragedią."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claires krop er fuld af ar, hun har smerter i ben og ryg, har det elendigt psykisk og er tom følelsesmæssigt. Efter en ulykke har hun skilt sig af med både mand, venner og terapeuter. Hun lukker kun sin trofaste husholderske ind, og af og til gartneren til lidt meningsløs sex. Men da en kvinde i terapigruppen begår selvmord, får Claires liv en anden drivkraft end den, der går ud på hele tiden at jage piller."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Fericire cu orice preț","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hilara Claire Bennett devine fascinată de sinuciderea unei femei. Pe măsură ce descoperă detaliile sinuciderii Ninei, se luptă și cu tragedia personală."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Cake: Uma Razão para Viver","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Simmons é uma mulher traumatizada e depressiva, que busca ajuda em um grupo para pessoas com dores crônicas. Lá, ela descobre o suicídio de um dos membros do grupo, Nina. Claire fica obcecada pela história desta mulher, e começa a investigar a sua vida. Aos poucos, começa a desenvolver uma relação inesperada com o ex-marido de Nina, Roy."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Торта","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Дженифър Анистън все още е свързвана предимно с \"Приятели\" и комедийните си роли, но това има потенциала да се промени с предстоящия \"Торта\". В своите 98 минути драмата, която след премиерата си в Торонто породи догадки за номинация за \"Оскар\" в категорията за главна женска роля, разказва за Клер (Анистън), която след катастрофа посещава терапевтична група за хора с хронични болки. Зависима от болкоуспокояващите, разведена, често посягаща към алкохола, без приятели и винаги отговаряща със сарказъм, героинята на Анистън търси пътя си без да има очевиден изход от ситуацията. Събитието, което я провокира да преосмисли живота си, е самоубийството на член на групата. \"Торта\", на който Анистън е също така копродуцент, се очаква по кината в Северна Америка и Европа на все още необявена дата през първата половина на 2015 г."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Cake　ケーキ　～悲しみが通り過ぎるまで～","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"主人公のクレア・ベネットが、妻に先立たれた男に恋とも同情ともつかぬ感情を抱いて近づいたり、かと思えばその亡くなった妻の生々しい幻影に付きまとわれたりする、どことなく滑稽な彼女の日常を描く。介護人でもあるしっかり者の家政婦に支えられながら、クレアが人間的なつながりを探し求め、自分を許せるようになるまでを綴った救済と再生の物語。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hoci v dome, kde žije a kde sa o ňu stará jej mexická slúžka Silvana, nie je obkľúčená duchmi svojej tragickej minulosti, ktorá sa jej s každým pohybom odzrkadľuje v bolestivom úškľabku na tvári, hľadá Claire Bennett útechu a psychickú podporu v Skupine chronických bolestí, ktorej stretnutia pravidelne navštevuje. Tu spoznáva i nešťastný osud končiaci tragickou samovraždou iba tridsaťjedenročnej Niny Collins, korá svojím egoistickým činom zruinovala život svojmu mužovi Royovi a ich synčekovi Caseymu. Zapíjajúc antidepresíva a lieky, ktoré zmierňujú jej bolesť alkoholom, Claire čoraz väčšmi prenasleduje duch nebohej Niny, s manželom ktorej postupne nadväzuje bolestivý vzťah..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Cake: Una razón para vivir","runtime":102,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Claire (Jennifer Aniston) tiene prácticamente una vida llena de problemas. Lucha día a día para lidiar con el dolor que la está debilitando y después de su divorcio, la última cosa que ella necesita en su vida es el trauma añadido del suicidio de Nina (Anna Kendrik), una mujer del grupo de apoyo al que ella acude. Mientras Claire lucha por tranquilizarse y combatir los desafíos del día a día, establece un vínculo con su ama de llaves y el ex marido de Nina. Mientras investiga las causas del suicidio de la mujer, se ve incapaz de dar respuesta a sus dudas, sin embargo sí que empieza a servirle de ayuda para apaciguar su propia angustia y comenzar así un lento proceso de curación."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Pyragas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Klerė Simons - nemaloni, bet žavi paramos grupės narė. Dėl padidėjusių jos lėtinių skausmų po nelaimės ir dar vienos narės savižudybės ji tampa tiesiog nepakenčiama, todėl yra išmetama iš grupės. Po šio įvykio ji bando atskleisti Ninos (buvusios grupės narės) vižudybės detales, pradeda plėtoti skaudžius santykius su jos vyru, pati kovodama su savo asmenine šeimos tragedija."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"الغفران حبة مرة تبتلعها.","homepage":"","overview":"بعد رؤى أحد أعضاء مجموعتها الداعمة التي قتلت نفسها ، تبحث امرأة تعاني أيضًا من ألم مزمن عن أرمل المنتحر."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"케이크","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Razlogi za življenje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"蛋糕的滋味","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一名女子在一場重大車禍中存活了下來，但卻讓她留下了慢性疼痛的後遺症，最後與互助會中另一位尋找愛妻死亡真相的鰥夫展開了一場難分難解的愛戀。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"蛋糕的滋味","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一名女子在一場重大車禍中存活了下來，但卻讓她留下了慢性疼痛的後遺症，最後與互助會中另一位尋找愛妻死亡真相的鰥夫展開了一場難分難解的愛戀。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":102,"tagline":"Le pardon est une pilule amère à avaler.","homepage":"","overview":"Claire Bennett va mal. Il n’y a qu’à voir ses cicatrices et ses grimaces de douleur dès qu’elle fait un geste pour comprendre qu’elle souffre physiquement. Elle ne parvient guère mieux à dissimuler son mal‐être affectif."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"55d381edc3a3683b83000414","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/55d381edc3a3683b83000414","author":"Reno","content":"$11","created_at":"2015-08-18T19:05:17.382Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:18:26.967Z","author_details":{"name":"Reno","rating":7,"username":"Rangan","avatar_path":"/6ZpVUJzqXMzH35VprEtnX0sNI3.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":267872,"adult":false,"title":"Korengal","video":false,"overview":"Korengal picks up where Restrepo left off; the same men, the same valley, the same commanders, but a very different look at the experience of war.","genre_ids":[99,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7161,"vote_count":84,"poster_path":"/kTJF1NOX0HYCRmiuM42F7qjZOxW.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-30","vote_average":6.565,"backdrop_path":"/lqThNsJ3NUsIZDLvbts6n9YESVr.jpg","original_title":"Korengal","original_language":"en"},{"id":248543,"adult":false,"title":"Good Luck","video":false,"overview":"After several behavior problems, teenager John is admitted to a psychiatric clinic by his family. There he meets Judith, for who he soon falls in love. The problem is that she does not have long to live and they know it. This shall not prevent the emergence of a great romance in the clinic.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9609,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/6xSdSVOtSqmqCmerYsxuLYyHdep.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-30","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/zWHM8DzbIJ1xxOgmAg28yJ9N3X7.jpg","original_title":"Boa Sorte","original_language":"pt"},{"id":16437,"adult":false,"title":"Cyborg 2","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2074, the cybernetics market is dominated by two rival companies: USA's Pinwheel Robotics and Japan's Kobayashi Electronics. Cyborgs are commonplace, used for anything from soldiers to prostitutes. Casella Reese is a prototype cyborg developed for corporate espionage and assassination. She is filled with a liquid explosive called Glass Shadow. Pinwheel plans to eliminate the entire Kobayashi board of directors by using Casella","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7529,"vote_count":144,"poster_path":"/hYNJ4KNMVaVgR5JAqC5qlgbJEmJ.jpg","release_date":"1993-11-24","vote_average":4.313,"backdrop_path":"/wyF3MzxcLZyJnEYZsp6XdPvpsdc.jpg","original_title":"Cyborg 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":283536,"adult":false,"title":"Ned Rifle","video":false,"overview":"Henry’s and Fay's son Ned sets out to find and kill his father for destroying his mother's life. But his aims are frustrated by the troublesome Susan, whose connection to Henry predates even his arrival in the lives of the Grim family.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7311,"vote_count":53,"poster_path":"/j6jVGR420EVgGlbPxE29dRk1GVU.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-01","vote_average":5.783,"backdrop_path":"/5grGtR5pXmOjFWKQlh83dGEhOnk.jpg","original_title":"Ned Rifle","original_language":"en"},{"id":191566,"adult":false,"title":"Crazy Kind of Love","video":false,"overview":"While re-evaluating her life, a mother relies on her stoner son and his awkward brother to keep life interesting. When an unlikely romance blossoms between the youngest son and the girl next door, she realizes the key to her happiness can be found where she least expects it.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6361,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/fFy97WBoUyGqlUVMh5A9YcJZsh7.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-31","vote_average":5.435,"backdrop_path":"/lY34oYh7u5BQrXcPEekKzoChIEK.jpg","original_title":"Crazy Kind of Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":1731,"adult":false,"title":"Helen","video":false,"overview":"On the outside, Helen has it all – a loving family and a successful career – but when her suppressed mental illness resurfaces, the world crumbles around her. Crippled by depression, Helen finds solace through her friendship with Mathilda, a kindred spirit struggling with bipolar disorder.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3973,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/wEs97E6NlySjkMEWsDYs0BhQ9Mw.jpg","release_date":"2009-11-26","vote_average":6.469,"backdrop_path":"/zeyplZ6isJArkhItcCHTokz2zFC.jpg","original_title":"Helen","original_language":"en"},{"id":340361,"adult":false,"title":"Florida","video":false,"overview":"Although he's now eighty years old, Claude Lherminier is still as imposing as he ever was. But his bouts of forgetfulness and confusion are becoming increasingly frequent. Even so, he stubbornly refuses to admit that anything is wrong. Carole, his oldest daughter, wages a daily and taxing battle to ensure that he's not left on his own. Claude suddenly decides on a whim to go to Florida. What lies behind this sudden trip?","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5979,"vote_count":77,"poster_path":"/9i91hzKVphqDPFUc8roQWygP5pZ.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-12","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/1SMBTYIj5KZ3p4vP1EbkaixYxLY.jpg","original_title":"Floride","original_language":"fr"},{"id":262642,"adult":false,"title":"Miss Sixty","video":false,"overview":"Now that we’re all living longer and “40 is the new 30,” why can’t 60 be the new 40? That’s what Louise and Frans think when they embark on bold new life adventures. Louise is a molecular biologist who decides to make a withdrawal from the sperm bank and have a baby. Meanwhile, gallery owner Frans decides to re-boot his career by finding the hottest new talent on the art scene. While attempting to recapture their lost youth and avoid total ridicule, Louise and Frans accidentally cross paths.","genre_ids":[10770,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3768,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/eYgNRgune5Z90IAZ8wG2NVf3nhW.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-24","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/3FejPxy6NJby3xMpYUv7l4M9VB0.jpg","original_title":"Miss Sixty","original_language":"de"},{"id":7509,"adult":false,"title":"Water","video":false,"overview":"The year is 1938, and Mahatma Gandhi's groundbreaking philosophies are sweeping across India, but 8-year-old Chuyia, newly widowed, must go to live with other outcast widows on an ashram. Her presence transforms the ashram as she befriends two of her compatriots.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7524,"vote_count":120,"poster_path":"/tdg6JKcqjS7szenmabGAbe5RGdN.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/qHZoqGqV6sH9wmzZhWnrTUEbWn8.jpg","original_title":"Water","original_language":"en"},{"id":91088,"adult":false,"title":"The King of Pigs","video":false,"overview":"Two friends, Jung Jong-suk and Hwang Kyung-min, meet after several years and talk about their time in school, which left them scarred.","genre_ids":[16,53,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9047,"vote_count":82,"poster_path":"/o93tMT3eyeOXBZ8F8TiGQWUq3Ta.jpg","release_date":"2011-11-03","vote_average":6.061,"backdrop_path":"/qEKkA07NBx2FPpciIXZQrTkEvXi.jpg","original_title":"돼지의 왕","original_language":"ko"},{"id":152273,"adult":false,"title":"The Sarnos: A Life in Dirty Movies","video":false,"overview":"A love story about the legendary sexploitation director Joe Sarno and his loyal wife and business partner Peggy. The film relates their part in the history of sex film, their lives between New York and Sweden, and their struggle to produce one last erotic film.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3154,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/dHQLef3s9KLsnAUCjK8rRCsy0cn.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-27","vote_average":5.895,"backdrop_path":"/pQTyYs1mxa0OJ3iLowTb6DlQql6.jpg","original_title":"The Sarnos: A Life in Dirty Movies","original_language":"en"},{"id":338636,"adult":false,"title":"Visit, or Memories and Confessions","video":false,"overview":"A long-hidden, personal doc about leaving a beloved house by the late, revered Portuguese director Manoel de Oliveira.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1671,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/1tMlCorBC5SRtQm5Nz6kakABH4.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-04","vote_average":7.467,"backdrop_path":"/tE2m3BGyiUX7tY6meabWOYZKpDR.jpg","original_title":"Visita ou Memórias e Confissões","original_language":"pt"},{"id":267579,"adult":false,"title":"The Ardor","video":false,"overview":"Kaí is a mysterious shaman who emerges from the Rio Paraná to help a poor farmer and his daughter, who are threatened by a band of cold-blooded mercenaries hired to force them to sell their land.","genre_ids":[37,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5782,"vote_count":36,"poster_path":"/yWifXtBV2xeXVOZj0hiqA7ToVbj.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-14","vote_average":4.778,"backdrop_path":"/lHG1aZjmaaoeZxsnzvvplEtnIbe.jpg","original_title":"Ardor","original_language":"es"},{"id":40490,"adult":false,"title":"Man of the House","video":false,"overview":"Ben Archer is not happy. His mother, Sandy, has just met a man, and it looks like things are pretty serious. Driven by a fear of abandonment, Ben tries anything and everything to ruin the \"love bubble\" which surrounds his mom. However, after Ben and Jack's experiences in the Indian Guides, the two become much closer.","genre_ids":[35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6545,"vote_count":185,"poster_path":"/6bnOhhrrrq6RZhMgz4aGyqbJ9Wf.jpg","release_date":"1995-03-03","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/45XjLWOACuD9UcFZ5iFGtQPVlAW.jpg","original_title":"Man of the House","original_language":"en"},{"id":259956,"adult":false,"title":"About Alex","video":false,"overview":"When a group of old college friends reunite over a long weekend after one of them attempts suicide, old crushes and resentments shine light on their life decisions, and ultimately push friendships and relationships to the brink.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6625,"vote_count":161,"poster_path":"/dWn9qrUP8W3u2TXfBMa6TkLkoLt.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-08","vote_average":6.084,"backdrop_path":"/iHRdW8lutD87ycdwKYkFcDL5sKU.jpg","original_title":"About Alex","original_language":"en"},{"id":284293,"adult":false,"title":"Still Alice","video":false,"overview":"Alice Howland, happily married with three grown children, is a renowned linguistics professor who starts to forget words. When she receives a devastating diagnosis, Alice and her family find their bonds 