":"en"},{"id":291692,"adult":false,"title":"Brotherhood of Blades","video":false,"overview":"In the late Ming Dynasty, three sworn brothers who serve as the imperial secret police are dispatched to hunt down Wei Zhongxian, a eunuch politician who had been forced to resign from his influential post and exiled from Beijing. The brothers return successfully from their quest, only to find that their task was but the beginning of a strange conspiracy.","genre_ids":[10749,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1567,"vote_count":181,"poster_path":"/d2mXV6VXqpxxv5Zet9xc2rKVpJz.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-07","vote_average":6.738,"backdrop_path":"/hnVbBBQMztst5gbmXsp7oyQTCaY.jpg","original_title":"绣春刀","original_language":"zh"}],"similar_content":[{"id":156,"adult":false,"title":"Wilbur Wants to Kill Himself","video":false,"overview":"The strange comedy film of two close brothers; one, Wilbur, who wants to kill himself, and the other, Harbour, who tries to prevent this. When their father dies leaving them his bookstore they meet a woman who makes their lives a bit better yet with a bit more trouble as well.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":0.5468,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/bRrHJbr8kMb849IKBZ0RBk2Vmte.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-08","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/2bCcbNyB1g5F8CXqABo0JsNig73.jpg","original_title":"Wilbur begår selvmord","original_language":"da"},{"id":159,"adult":false,"title":"Maybe... Maybe Not","video":false,"overview":"The heterosexual man Axel is thrown out of his girlfriends home for cheating and ends up moving in with a gay man. Axel learns the advantages of living with gay men even though they are attracted to him and when his girlfriend wants him back he must make a tough decision.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.6747,"vote_count":117,"poster_path":"/2TcZBHcseRXLxNq2RXnKIsbKZwi.jpg","release_date":"1994-10-05","vote_average":6.218,"backdrop_path":"/cLOyix71NJwkfwt77bnmmy9ibJO.jpg","original_title":"Der bewegte Mann","original_language":"de"},{"id":175,"adult":false,"title":"The Big Blue","video":false,"overview":"Childhood friends Jacques and Enzo share a passion for the danger of free diving. Professional diver Jacques opted to follow in the footsteps of his father, who died at sea when Jacques was a boy; to the bewilderment of scientists, Jacques harbors a remarkable ability to adjust his heart rate and breathing pattern in the water, so that his vital signs more closely resemble that of dolphins than men. As Enzo persuades a reluctant Jacques to compete against him in a free diving contest -- determining who can dive deeper and longer without scuba gear -- Jacques meets Johana, a beautiful American insurance investigator, and finds that he must choose between his love for her and his love of the sea.","genre_ids":[10749,12,18],"popularity":3.0097,"vote_count":1535,"poster_path":"/3t5t7yaFiTJQlqxiTkXJMFZdkh3.jpg","release_date":"1988-05-10","vote_average":7.445,"backdrop_path":"/1J28PJOkusMN5Ab9Q3oF310e11k.jpg","original_title":"Le Grand Bleu","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1292040,"adult":false,"title":"It's Hard to Be Iben","video":true,"overview":"Iben attempts to deal with the death of her parents, in her own way.","genre_ids":[27,35,18],"popularity":0.1713,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/6kqwF0xkFXjXhRi2CgVYRmpOjlf.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-11","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Det er tøft å være Iben","original_language":"no"},{"id":659,"adult":false,"title":"The Tin Drum","video":false,"overview":"In 1924, Oskar Matzerath is born in the Free City of Danzig. At age three, he falls down a flight of stairs and stops growing. In 1939, World War II breaks out.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":5.569,"vote_count":518,"poster_path":"/tm408GMyQqfqFJ7MKCkwc5uQ3wi.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-02","vote_average":6.94,"backdrop_path":"/uZJjc4hMgckb3H3tVkTmbmcBhIT.jpg","original_title":"Die Blechtrommel","original_language":"de"},{"id":695,"adult":false,"title":"Short Cuts","video":false,"overview":"Many loosely connected characters cross paths in this film, based on the stories of Raymond Carver. Waitress Doreen Piggot accidentally runs into a boy with her car. Soon after walking away, the child lapses into a coma. While at the hospital, the boy's grandfather tells his son, Howard, about his past affairs. Meanwhile, a baker starts harassing the family when they fail to pick up the boy's birthday cake.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":1.7833,"vote_count":660,"poster_path":"/nAEBc3g9bHAcF9whKFMfIxHxVwn.jpg","release_date":"1993-10-01","vote_average":7.195,"backdrop_path":"/a0OjGWE9ru1OlKLBujbz3mAYYxU.jpg","original_title":"Short Cuts","original_language":"en"},{"id":746,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Emperor","video":false,"overview":"A dramatic history of Pu Yi, the last of the Emperors of China, from his lofty birth and brief reign in the Forbidden City, the object of worship by half a billion people; through his abdication, his decline and dissolute lifestyle; his exploitation by the invading Japanese, and finally to his obscure existence as just another peasant worker in the People's Republic.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":5.1709,"vote_count":1867,"poster_path":"/7TILJhdeJAaEyDiwvJZMo9SQBoe.jpg","release_date":"1987-10-04","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/k29qVmwWwR0i5A1UMIws1Vmv6hV.jpg","original_title":"The Last Emperor","original_language":"en"},{"id":421619,"adult":false,"title":"The Constitution","video":false,"overview":"Four very different people live in the same building but avoid each other because of differences in how they live their lives, what they believe in, and where they come from. They would probably never exchange a word, but misfortune pushes them towards each other. Their lives entangle in ways that profoundly challenge deep-held beliefs and prejudices surrounding material status, sexual orientation, nationality and religion.  Slowly, and even painfully, they begin to open up to each other and recognize the essential humanity each of them possesses.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4549,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/6OkmN8jhqsoL0Uu9hpsoDnhpXLF.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-06","vote_average":6.567,"backdrop_path":"/zPBb2YI5ybUg9NcdEtFwfXeA9IM.jpg","original_title":"Ustav Republike Hrvatske","original_language":"hr"},{"id":1962,"adult":false,"title":"Love in Thoughts","video":false,"overview":"A posthumous look at the last days of Guenther's life as he, his best friend, and his sister let loose on a four-day binge of alcohol, drugs, and sex.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.8287,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/iOiPogpC9IF0MLBSiSrP9WIJ9nD.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-12","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/h74qqBEGMvjmWAgYFQAFOn82KYq.jpg","original_title":"Was nützt die Liebe in Gedanken","original_language":"de"},{"id":2021,"adult":false,"title":"Jack & Sarah","video":false,"overview":"Jack always lands on his feet. He lands on his feet when he marries the beautiful Sarah. He lands on his feet when he buys a luxurious new home. However, when Sarah goes into labour, he takes a tumble down the stairs and lands on his head. When he comes around he discovers he is the proud father of a baby girl, but deficient in the spouse department to the tune of 1.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":5.8811,"vote_count":56,"poster_path":"/yWMj1KMfnixB35qa2IZKniHF4sn.jpg","release_date":"1995-06-02","vote_average":6.705,"backdrop_path":"/2LDY0auGo25vERpruG5PV9I1OMJ.jpg","original_title":"Jack & Sarah","original_language":"en"},{"id":880,"adult":false,"title":"Antonia's Line","video":false,"overview":"After World War II, Antonia and her daughter, Danielle, go back to their Dutch hometown, where Antonia's late mother has bestowed a small farm upon her. There, Antonia settles down and joins a tightly-knit but unusual community. Those around her include quirky friend Crooked Finger, would-be suitor Bas and, eventually for Antonia, a granddaughter and great-granddaughter who help create a strong family of empowered women.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.7991,"vote_count":140,"poster_path":"/nUCVi6bBIL7LGC61nYaCqikAhIA.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-21","vote_average":6.904,"backdrop_path":"/sOkUBkwq21ZEThCX7wboY2Xl3m5.jpg","original_title":"Antonia","original_language":"nl"},{"id":881,"adult":false,"title":"A Few Good Men","video":false,"overview":"When cocky military lawyer Lt. Daniel Kaffee and his co-counsel, Lt. Cmdr. JoAnne Galloway, are assigned to a murder case, they uncover a hazing ritual that could implicate high-ranking officials such as shady Col. Nathan Jessep.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":5.3275,"vote_count":4028,"poster_path":"/rLOk4z9zL1tTukIYV56P94aZXKk.jpg","release_date":"1992-12-11","vote_average":7.542,"backdrop_path":"/H40nWdJngUc6gtytMAbElm9HOu.jpg","original_title":"A Few Good Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":890,"adult":false,"title":"Brother of Sleep","video":false,"overview":"In the beginning of the 19th century, Johannes Elias Alder is born in a small village in the Austrian mountains. While growing up he is considered strange by the other villagers and discovers his love of music, especially rebuilding and playing the organ at the village church. After experiencing an \"acoustic wonder\", his eye color changes and he can hear even the most subtle sounds.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":3.7415,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/xMnI1UauGsAQxoraCiTGEab6jHZ.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-08","vote_average":6.591,"backdrop_path":"/ioOJOynKH49uTRXYhKDgGJkHDud.jpg","original_title":"Schlafes Bruder","original_language":"de"},{"id":899,"adult":false,"title":"Broken Blossoms or The Yellow Man and the Girl","video":false,"overview":"The love story of an abused English girl and a Chinese Buddhist in a time when London was a brutal and harsh place to live.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.9084,"vote_count":238,"poster_path":"/njwFIUL76zaRmPemnrZVmmTSCjz.jpg","release_date":"1919-05-13","vote_averag